[The etiology of this presumed waterborne illness is not clear. ProMED awaits more information from knowledgeable sources about the etiology of the cluster.

Landi Kotal, or Lwargai, is a town in the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa province of Pakistan and the administrative capital of Khyber District. It was one of the largest towns in the former Federally Administered Tribal Areas. - Mod.LL

